gate: OPEN
status: BLOCKED
blocked_on: front#1538 (Oleg Marcrest FE) must be merged to dev first
issue: https://github.com/CT-CROP/CROP-front/issues/1541
owner: Denis (denistka)
as_of: 2026-06-03
note: |
  search-hono#332 (MAR backend) already merged ✓.
  Waiting on Oleg's #1538. Local env ready (localhost:3000 + Cloud Run hono).
  Smoke checklist covers: /parts/brand/{slug} + /parts-diagrams/{slug} + assembly
  for all 4 brands at 375px and 1280px.
sprint: S06
track: A
task: A3
title: "test(brands): 4-brand end-to-end smoke — brand page + model grid + diagram path"
repos: [crop-front, crop-search-hono]
priority: high
refs:
  - meetup-02-06-26 ("means they have to have brand landing pages... interface is working cleanly")
  - S06-A1, S06-A2 (must be merged first)
requires: [NEXTJS_VERCEL_FRONTEND, BUN_HONO_CLOUDRUN]

impact: |
  The team committed to delivering 4 brands to production next Friday. Without a
  structured smoke-test checklist, bugs surface in prod in front of ownership (the
  presentation John mentioned). This task defines what "production ready" means for
  each brand and documents the test run so Denis + Vova can sign off.

description: |
  For each brand {ferris, ventrac, mchale, marcrest} verify the following manually
  in the dev environment (crop-dev.app or localhost), then record pass/fail below.
  Denis runs each scenario locally before Vova does final check.

  Brand landing (/parts/brand/{slug}):
  - Page renders without 500/404
  - Brand name + logo visible in hero header
  - At least 1 TypeCard from hono equipment-types (or graceful empty-state if data
    not yet seeded — must NOT be a broken layout)
  - "Search all parts" CTA leads to /parts?manufacturer={vendorCode}
  - Serial search widget renders
  - robots meta = noindex,follow (not noindex,nofollow)

  Parts-diagrams brand page (/parts-diagrams/{slug}):
  - Page renders without 500/404
  - Model group grid shows (or graceful empty-state if hono returns empty)
  - Each model card links to /parts-diagrams/{slug}/{modelCode}

  Assembly page (/parts-diagrams/{slug}/{modelCode} for at least 1 model):
  - Schematic viewer loads
  - BOM table renders at least 1 part
  - "Add to cart" on a BOM row works (or visible if user not signed in)

scope:
  in:
    - Manual test run checklist (to be filled by Denis during QA)
    - Any bug fixes discovered during the smoke run that are ≤ 10 lines (absorb inline)
    - Larger bugs: open as GitHub issues with impact statement, link from this task
  out:
    - New feature work
    - Automated Playwright e2e (separate task if scope allows — not V2 blocker)

invariants:
  - Test run must mirror prod conditions: use dev Vercel deploy, not localhost build
  - Each brand must be tested independently (no cross-brand data sharing assumption)

acceptance:
  Pass criteria for "production ready":
  - All 3 pages above return 200 for all 4 brands in dev environment
  - No JS console errors (aside from pre-existing known issues — document exceptions)
  - No broken layouts at 375px (mobile) and 1280px (desktop) viewport

smoke-checklist:
  # Fill in ✓/✗ + note during QA run:
  ferris:
    brand_landing: ""
    parts_diagrams: ""
    assembly_page: ""
  ventrac:
    brand_landing: ""
    parts_diagrams: ""
    assembly_page: ""
  mchale:
    brand_landing: ""
    parts_diagrams: ""
    assembly_page: ""
  marcrest:
    brand_landing: ""
    parts_diagrams: ""
    assembly_page: ""

dep: A1, A2
output: this file (smoke-checklist filled in) + bug issues if any found
